**  MSG
E-01 RECEIVING CO. ISN'T INPUT
E-02 INPUT ONLY NUMBER INTO CLAUSE
E-03 THERE IS NOT THIS CODE IN DETAIL M/F
E-04 FACTORY CODE OF RECEIVING CO. ISN'T INPUT
E-05 RECEIVING CODE OF RECEIVING CO. ISN'T INPUT
E-06 USER PART NO ISN'T INPUT
E-07 YEAR, MONTH, OR DAY OF THE DATE REVERSING  ISN'T RIGHT
E-08 UPDATE INST IS 0= CANCEL 1= CHANGE SELECT EITHER OF THOSE
E-09 PUTTING OUT LINE THAT REVERSING,THERE ISN'T ODR RECEIPT DATA
E-10 CHANGING LINE THAT REVERSING, THERE ISN'T ORDER RECEIPT DATA
E-11 IT ISN'T POSSIBLE TO ADD ORDER RECEIPT DATA
E-12 CUSTOMER ISN'T INPUT
E-13 FACTORY OF CUSTOMER ISN'T INPUT
E-14 RECEIVING OF CUSTOMER ISN'T INPUT
E-15 IFAOSHO ISN'T IN ORDER RECEIPT M/F, CAN'T UPDATE DATA
E-16 INTRAL COMPANY PART NO ISN'T INPUT
E-17 INPUT UNIT PRICE INSTRUCTION IS EITHER OF 01239
E-18 SELECT UNIT PRICE FORM <VOLUME PRODUCTION =A  EXCEPTION =B>
E-19 DELIVERY NUMBER ISN'T INPUT
E-20 DELIVERY NUMBER UNIT   <C G / K>
E-21 STATEMENT OF DELIVERY INSTRUCTION MUST BE <1 BLANK>
E-22 DELIVERY DATE ISN'T INPUT
E-23 ORDER RECEIPT INSTRUCTION IS <J L K / A / W>
E-24 SELECT  RECORD INSTRUCTION IS EITHER OF <BLANK J I  S / G>
E-25 SHIP ODR IS VOLUME PROD =G.X.A LIMITATION =Z TRIAL MFG =S
E-26 APPOINTED STATEMENT OF DELIVERY IS <1 3 G H / BLANK>
E-27 TAG INSTRUCTION IS <1 BLANK>
E-28 DATA INSTRUCTION IS <1 BLANK>
E-29  POOL INSTRUCTION IS <1 B BLANK>
E-30 ASSEMBLED FORM   < A-1234567 B-123456 C-123 D-1 >
E-31 SHIPMENT PRODUCTION ORDER DATE ISN'T INPUT
E-32 EXECUTED INQUIRY AND UPDATE,BUT THERE ISN'T ODR RECEIPT DATA
E-33 YOU CAN'T UPDATE IT INFORM YOU TO COMPUTATION ROOM.
